attach.desc: Gives the address of an associated document for the event.

categories.desc: Gives the name of a category or tag that the event could be classified as.

class.desc: Gives the access classification of the information regarding the event.

comment.desc: Gives a comment regarding the event.

contact.desc: Gives the contact information for the event.

created.desc: Gives the date and time at which the event information was first created in a calendaring system.

description.desc: Gives a detailed description of the event.

dtend.desc: Gives the date and time by which the event ends.

dtstart.desc: Gives the date and time at which the event starts.

duration.desc: Gives the duration of the event.

exdate.desc: Gives a date and time at which the event does not occur despite the recurrence rules.

geo.desc: Gives the geographical position of the event.

last-modified.desc: Gives the date and time at which the event information was last modified in a calendaring system.

location.desc: Gives the location of the event.

rdate.desc: Gives a date and time at which the event recurs.

resources.desc: Gives a resource that will be needed for the event.

rrule.desc: Gives a rule for finding dates and times at which the event occurs.

sequence.desc: Gives a revision number for the event information.

status.desc: Gives the confirmation status of the event.

summary.desc: Gives a short summary of the event.

transp.desc: Gives whether the event is to be considered as consuming time on a calendar, for the purpose of free-busy time searches.

uid.desc: Gives a globally unique identifier corresponding to the event.

url.desc: Gives a URL for the event.

http://microformats.org/profile/hcard.desc: A person's or organization's contact information.
http://microformats.org/profile/hcard.label: vCard

adr.desc: Gives the delivery address of the person or organization.

country-name.desc: Gives the country name component of the delivery address of the person or organization.

extended-address.desc: Gives an additional component of the delivery address of the person or organization.

locality.desc: Gives the locality component (e.g. city) of the delivery address of the person or organization.

post-office-box.desc: Gives the post office box component of the delivery address of the person or organization.

postal-code.desc: Gives the postal code component of the delivery address of the person or organization.

region.desc: Gives the region component (e.g. state or province) of the delivery address of the person or organization.

street-address.desc: Gives the street address component of the delivery address of the person or organization.

type.desc: Gives the type of delivery address.

home.desc: Indicates a delivery address for a residence.

work.desc: Indicates a delivery address for a place of work.

agent.desc: Gives the contact information of another person who will act on behalf of the person or organization.

anniversary.desc: Gives the birth date of the person or organization.

bday.desc: Gives the birth date of the person or organization.

categories.desc: Gives the name of a category or tag that the person or organization could be classified as.

email.desc: Gives the e-mail address of the person or organization.

fn.desc: Gives the formatted text corresponding to the name of the person or organization.

gender-identity.desc: Gives the gender identity of the person.

geo.desc: Gives the geographical position of the person or organization.

impp.desc: Gives a URL for instant messaging and presence protocol communications with the person or organization.

kind.desc: Describes what kind of contact the item represents.

group.desc: Indicates multiple entities (e.g. a mailing list).

individual.desc: Indicates a single entity (e.g. a person).

location.desc: Indicates a geographical place (e.g. an office building).

org.desc: Indicates a single entity that is not a person (e.g. a company).

lang.desc: Gives a language understood by the person or organization.

logo.desc: Gives the logo of the person or organization.

member.desc: Gives a URL that represents a member of the group.

n.desc: Gives the structured name of the person or organization.

additional-name.desc: Gives the any additional names of the person.

family-name.desc: Gives the family name of the person, or the full name of the organization.

given-name.desc: Gives the given-name of the person.

honorific-prefix.desc: Gives the honorific prefix of the person.

honorific-suffix.desc: Gives the honorific suffix of the person.

nickname.desc: Gives the nickname of the person or organization.

note.desc: Gives supplemental information or a comment about the person or organization.

org.desc: Gives the name and units of the organization.

organization-name.desc: Gives the name of the organization.

organization-unit.desc: Gives the name of the organization unit.

photo.desc: Gives a photograph of the person or organization.

related.desc: Gives a relationship to another entity.

rel.desc: Gives the relationship between the entity and the related entity.

agent.desc: Another entity that acts on behalf of this entity.

url.desc: Gives the URL for the related entity.

rev.desc: Gives the revision date and time of the contact information.

role.desc: Gives the role, occupation, or business category of the person or organization.

sex.desc: Gives the biological sex of the person.

sound.desc: Gives a sound file relating to the person or organization.

tel.desc: Gives the telephone number of the person or organization.

type.desc: Gives the type of telephone number.

pager.desc: Indicates a paging device telephone number.

text.desc: Indicates that the telephone number supports text messages (SMS).

textphone.desc: Indicates a telecommunication device for people with hearing or speech difficulties.

video.desc: Indicates a video conferencing telephone number.

work.desc: Indicates a telephone number for a place of work.

value.desc: Gives the actual telephone number of the person or organization.

title.desc: Gives the job title, functional position or function of the person or organization.

tz.desc: Gives the time zone of the person or organization.

uid.desc: Gives a globally unique identifier corresponding to the person or organization.

url.desc: Gives a URL relating to the person or organization.

http://n.whatwg.org/work.desc: A work (e.g. an article, an image, a video, a song, etc).
http://n.whatwg.org/work.label: Licensing works

author.desc: Gives the name or contact information of one of the authors or creators of the work.

license.desc: Identifies one of the licenses under which the work is available.

title.desc: Gives the name of the work.
